data.description: Here is a great starter home for YOU! Plenty of storage through out this property in the home - basement - and garage and workshop! You will enjoy 3 bedrooms, single bath, large living and dining room and much more! First floor laundry is a real plus with the stackable washer & dryer included! Spacious 1 car garage will house your SUV and other equipment.  There is also a workshop on the back of the garage for much more usable space. Finally you will enjoy the nice covered porch overlooking the fenced back yard!  A perfect spot to enjoy warmer evenings! Come take a peak to see how well this home will fit your dreams!
